title: Rittal Blue e+ temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/rittal
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Temperature sensors of a Rittal Blue e+ cooling unit: internal, ambient
 and (if connected) the external temperature sensor.

 By default the warning/alarm thresholds configured on the appliance itself
 are used as upper levels; these can be overridden with the {Rittal Blue e+
 temperature} ruleset. The value is also emitted as performance data.

 Sensors reporting status {not available} are not discovered.

item:
 The Blue e+ device name plus the sensor, e.g. "Blue e Plus 1 Internal".

inventory:
 One service per connected temperature sensor of each Blue e+ unit.
